testOwnableInheritance().details: Verifies registry inherits Ownable and owner is set correctly

testPreventDuplicateTokenNetwork().details: Verifies that creating a TokenNetwork for the same token twice reverts

testRejectInvalidToken().details: Verifies that attempting to create TokenNetwork with non-ERC20 contract reverts

testRejectZeroAddressToken().details: Verifies that attempting to create TokenNetwork with zero address reverts

testTokenNetworkCreatedEvent().details: Verifies event is emitted with correct parameters

testWhitelistDisabledByDefault().details: Verifies whitelist enforcement is disabled on deployment

testAddAllowedToken().notice: Test owner can add token to whitelist

testCreateTokenNetwork().notice: Test successful TokenNetwork creation for valid ERC20 token

testDisabledWhitelistAllowsAll().notice: Test disabled whitelist allows all tokens

testMultipleTokenNetworks().notice: Test multiple TokenNetwork creation for different tokens

testRejectAddAllowedTokenByNonOwner().notice: Test non-owner cannot add token to whitelist

testRejectZeroAddressWhitelist().notice: Test reject zero address in addAllowedToken

testRemoveAllowedToken().notice: Test owner can remove token from whitelist

testWhitelistEnforcementAllowsWhiteliste.notice: Test whitelist enforcement allows whitelisted tokens
